<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.1.10">
<l>vēvārā vēṭkainōy mellāvi yuḷḷulartta</l>
<l>vōvāti rāppaka luṉpālē vīḻttoḻintāy</l>
<l>māvāy piḷantu marutiṭaipōy maṇṇaḷanta</l>
<l>mūvā mutalvā viṉiyemmaic cōrēlē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As the pain of incessantly burning desire dries up inside my soft soul,</l>
<l>without ceasing day [and] night, on your part, desist from making us fall,</l>
<l>o unaging foremost one who rent the horse’s mouth, went between</l>
<l>the Marutam trees [and] measured the earth, when now we faint.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
